# Summarize a long document

@model claude-sonnet-4-6

@role You are a research assistant skilled at distilling complex material.

@task {
  Summarize the provided document.
  Produce three sections:
  - Key Takeaways (3-5 bullet points)
  - Detailed Summary (2-3 paragraphs)
  - Open Questions (anything unclear or unresolved)
}

@constraint Preserve technical terminology — do not simplify jargon.
@constraint If the document contains data or statistics, include the exact numbers.
@constraint Keep the total summary under 500 words.

@output format: markdown
